Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:02:00.01,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've stopped caring about the changing of the seasons.{I ceased to care}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.42,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Shirasugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.48,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Shirasugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.87,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Last stop, Wakase...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:21.03,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Please wait for the express train, it will come after...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:32.26,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,How much meaning is there to the fact that it is spring right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:01.74,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,There's someone else I've fallen in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:06.26,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Oh... Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:44.10,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Tsubana. Tsubana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:48.99,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Please wait until the train comes to a complete stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm getting off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, student!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no... I'm so out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all I have about the next arranged marriage party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't have any particular questions, then I would like to end the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This party is restricted to members in their late 20's to early 30's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, someday I hope to bring down the membership age to include teens,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and have a party restricted to women in their teens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't a new restaurant open up in Kanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sorting the membership data files in the back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That face... that smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't show that to customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There should definitely be a demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From experience, men my age can only meet teenage girls in an unlawful way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it's "your" demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't there any opportunities to meet a female high school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm ho...me...{Or just use "tadaima" if you feel like being extra weeaboo, most people know it by now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't told about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you're going to be living with Nanoka starting tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show you Nanoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't remember her, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes I do... I do, but I don't remember her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a freshman in high school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's 15 years old. She is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone commutes from far away nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She can cut her commute time from two hours to one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it natural that we let her stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because you got dumped by your lover,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you don't intend on getting back together with mom, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:09.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a family member!{Or just "She's family!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.42,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,With my carefree life living with Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:24.12,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:33.86,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I have a mother and a sister who's 12 years younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please introduce her to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you thinking?{What the hell are you thinking?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why were you hiding something so important from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's basically like I don't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My parents got divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I met my mom, who took custody of her, a couple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I haven't seen my sister at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of partner are you interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I came while you're working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my lunch break anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to get the keys to my place{room} back.{More like place, "Heya" is often used to refer to apartments/etc as well as individual rooms}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it might be better during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really letting me go easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just accepted things so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just felt like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is all I meant to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, have you ever loved anyone from the bottom of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, have you ever loved anyone from the bottom of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.54,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Then what should I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the party, we're planning to have three events,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so if we could divide the food and have it brought out to match the timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, concerning the audio equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. There are for the place next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much.  Don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:50.38,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,What do I say to a woman that says she has another man...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.33,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,What should I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a great view.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a place that kind of hurts for a bachelor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you broke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so cool about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what she dislikes about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll give these to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try inviting that girl you broke up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you guys will get back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell's going to get back together with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm glad. {Or maybe "Thank goodness"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a naughty boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asking out high school girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm interrupting your date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wrong too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is good. I was waiting to meet a someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I came too early and I needed to kill time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meeting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. My father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. What would you like to ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be boring with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just broke up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I received it during my junior high graduation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from the person I liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't his second button.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.46,TL Note,,0,0,0,,{\a6}In Japan it is traditional upon graduating to give the second button from your school uniform to a girl you like
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I liked him since I was a first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like he's really handsome or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I really liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gathered up all my courage and confessed to him but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he's going out with a junior at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the window could open, I could throw it out from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say you're going to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still like him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then don't say that you're going to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to forget about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has someone that he's going out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We go to different{separate} high schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll never even see each other anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you love someone so straightforward and honestly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just got dumped too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's really different from your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My feelings totally cooled off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I don't really know if I really loved her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should definitely treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the feelings that you have inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since I got rejected, I kept walking with my head down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I didn't notice the flowers blooming at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you stopped me back at the train station,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed it for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The petals were falling like snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and for a moment I couldn't tell where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:11.35,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,That's the same for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:16.65,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Where is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:20.50,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,this place that I've always been at?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.78,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Is being here unforgivable?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here too, Koshiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since you siblings have gotten together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you two recognize each other right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong with the two of you? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we have for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brother? {Onii-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little sister.
